<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Student Portal</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset basic styling */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #f5f5f5, #e8eaf6);
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Header styling */
        header {
            background-color: #4a148c;
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }

        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        nav {
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
        }

        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 1rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: #fbc02d;
        }

        /* Container styling */
        .container {
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        /* Section styling */
        h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            color: #4a148c;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-in-out;
            background: #ede7f6;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .section {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        /* Text content styling */
        .text-content {
            flex: 2;
            padding: 15px;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #424242;
            transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
        }

        /* Image container styling */
        .image-container {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .image-container img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        /* Footer styling */
        footer {
            background-color: #4a148c;
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        footer a {
            color: #fbc02d;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-20px);
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .section {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .image-container {
                margin-top: 1rem;
                display: block;
            }

            .card {
                font-size: 1rem;
                padding: 1rem;
            }

            nav a {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <header>
        <h1>About Student Portal</h1>
        <nav>
            <a href="#overview">Overview</a>
            <a href="#features">Features</a>
            <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="container">

        <h2 id="overview">Overview</h2>
        <div class="section">
            <div class="text-content">
                <div class="card">
                    The Student Portal is a modern platform designed to simplify and centralize access to essential tools,
                    services, and information for students. It empowers students to manage personal details efficiently, track
                    their academic activities, and stay informed with real-time updates and notifications. With an intuitive
                    interface, the portal ensures a seamless experience, enabling students to navigate effortlessly through its
                    features. By integrating all critical tools into a single platform, it eliminates the hassle of managing
                    multiple systems. Whether it's customizing your dashboard, accessing secure academic resources, or staying
                    updated with announcements, the Student Portal is designed to enhance productivity and convenience in daily
                    student life.  
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="image-container">
                <img
                    src="https://media.istockphoto.com/id/1364358545/photo/web-page-browser-of-social-media-page-vr-interface-on-the-laptop-computer.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=T53je0Lr1HNGzMyJ6gq-0Tk5bMEoIERClyhSffcqIfo="
                    alt="Overview Image">
            </div>
        </div>

        <h2 id="features">Key Features</h2>
        <div class="section">
            <div class="text-content">
                <div class="card">
                    <strong>Secure Access:</strong> With advanced encryption, your personal data and academic records are safeguarded, ensuring privacy and protection.
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <strong>Academic Progress Tracking:</strong> Easily monitor your course progress, grades, and upcoming deadlines to stay on top of your academic performance.
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <strong>Resource Access:</strong> Quickly access study materials, assignments, and academic resources, all in one convenient place.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="image-container">
                <img
                    src="https://www.kohezion.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/top-features-in-customer-inquiry-portals-1024x615.png"
                    alt="Features Image">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 About Student Portal. All rights reserved.</p>
        <a href="#top">Back to Top</a>
    </footer>

</body>

</html>
